~eZSNES Default Keys Player 1~0
  Up Arrow     - Up
  Down Arrow   - Down
  Left Arrow   - Left
  Right Arrow  - Right
  X            - A button
  Z            - B button
  S            - X button
  A            - Y button
  D            - Left Shoulder
  C            - Right Shoulder
  Enter        - Start
  Right Shift  - Select

